      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver, though it shows clear signs of its age and mileage. The exterior has some noticeable paint fading on the hood and roof, along with several scuffs and a small dent on the rear passenger door. Inside, the upholstery shows significant wear and some staining, and while the car runs and drives well, it will likely need a brake service and new tires in the near future. It\u2019s a solid, functional choice for someone looking for a budget-friendly option who doesn't mind a few cosmetic imperfections.",
