    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional find: a vehicle that looks, smells, and drives as if it just departed the showroom floor. This car has been pampered in a climate-controlled garage since day one and has never seen a drop of rain or winter salt. The exterior paint is deep and lustrous, completely free of swirls, stone chips, or imperfections, while the alloy wheels remain pristine without a single mark. Inside, the cabin is a time capsule; the premium leather upholstery remains taut and supple, and the high-tech infotainment system still has the factory-fresh responsiveness. Every button, switch, and mechanical component functions flawlessly. Accompanied by a comprehensive, folder-thick service history and both sets of original keys, this is a rare opportunity for a buyer who accepts nothing less than perfection. This isn't just a used car; it is a meticulously preserved piece of automotive excellence.",
