      "description": "Presenting a collector-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) in pristine, showroom condition. This example features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering linear power through six individual throttle bodies and a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual transmission. Mechanically flawless, the VANOS system has been proactively overhauled, and the rear subframe has been professionally reinforced to exceed factory specifications. The chassis remains incredibly taut, supported by a perfectly preserved suspension geometry and the M Variable Differential Lock for optimal lateral grip. Finished in its original Laguna Seca Blue with zero paint correction required, this is a turn-key investment for the discerning purist seeking peak atmospheric performance.",
